articles.title: Anthony Albanese: Australian PM announces engagement to Jodie Haydon - BBC.com
articles.description: Anthony Albanese is the first Australian leader to announce his engagement while in office.
articles.content:
By Tiffanie TurnbullBBC News, Sydney
Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese has announced his engagement to his partner of four years, Jodie Haydon.
